## THIS PROJECT HAS THREE MAIN PARTS.

### 1.HEADER FILES.
### 2.MAIN CPP FILES.
### 3.USER INTERFACE FILES.


### 1.HEADER FILES:

	Includes all and the Following.
			1.adminpage.h :  ## DEFINES CONNECTION TO MYSQL DATABASE AS A GLOBAL
					  FUNCTION.

					  ## IT ALSO DEFINES FUNCTIONS TO BUTTONS IN THE USER
					  INTERFACE OF THE ADMIN PAGE FORM.

					  ## DECLARATION OF CONSTRUCTORS AND DESTRUCTORS TO THE ADMIN PAGE.
					  ## DECLARATION OF CLASS ADMINPAGE.

			2.availableinventory.h : ## DEFINES FUNCTIONS OF BUTTONS TO THE AVAILABLE INVENTORY 							    FORM.
						  ## DECLARATION OF CONSTRUCTORS AND DESTRUCTORS.
					          ## DECLARATION OF CLASS AVAILABLE INVENTORY.



			3.edititems.h: ## DEFINES FUNCTIONS OF BUTTONS TO THE EDIT ITEMS FORM.
					## DEFINES POINTERS TO THE USER INTERFACE.
					## DECLARATION OF CLASS EDITITEMS.

			4.editteams.h:  ## DEFINES FUNCTIONS OF BUTTONS TO THE EDIT TEAMS FORM.
					## DEFINES POINTERS TO THE USER INTERFACE.
					## DECLARATION OF CLASS EDIT TEAMS. 
 							    
			5.mainview.h: ## BUTTONS DECLARED IN THE PRIVATE SLOTS IN THE MAIN CLASS MAINVIEW.
				       ## DECLARATION OF CLASS MAINVIEW.
					
			6.returnitems.h: ## BUTTONS DECLARED IN THE PRIVATE SLOTS IN THE MAIN CLASS RETURN 							ITEMS.
					  ## DECLARATION OF CLASS RETURN ITEMS.


### 2.MAIN CPP FILES.
	## IMPLEMENTATION OF THE MODEL AND THE CONTROLLER.
